{"view":"article","slug":"fmc-psb","category":"FMC","subcategory":null,"topDir":"FMC","title":{"en":"PSB (Pseudo Block)","zh":"伪砖 (PSB)"},"content":{"en":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>PSB (Pseudo Block)</strong></p><p>The case whose scramble is the inverse of the scramble of a case is called the <strong>inverse case</strong> of this case. </p><p>The pieces contained in a block-wise position are called <strong>PSB (pseudo block)</strong>. If a move sequence <em>P</em> with <em>n </em>moves solves every piece of PSB, then <em>P'</em> creates a solved block in inverse case of PSB. And this PSB is called <em>n</em>-move PSB. For example, in scramble <em>X</em> = L2 B2 L2 R' B' U2 L' U2 L2 F2 U2 F' L2 F' D B2, every piece of this 223 PSB can be solved using R B. Then for the inverse case whose scramble is <em>X'</em> = B2 D' F L2 F U2 F2 L2 U2 L U2 B R L2 B2 L2, B' R' creates a solved 223 block.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">      <img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">      <img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>scr = <em>X</em>, move R B solves 223 PSB pieces</p></td><td><p>scr = <em>X'</em>, move B' R' creates a 223 block</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>1-move PSB Examples</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PSF2L-1</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PS223</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PS123</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PS222</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PS122</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PS112</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>2-move PSB Examples</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R B</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R2 B2</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R' D</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong><u>Examples</u></strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F' D' B' D' F L2 D' L2 D L B L D\">F' D' B' D' F L2 D' L2 D L B L D</span></p><p>L' B' // PSF2L-1</p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(B') // F2L-1\">(B') // F2L-1</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"B' U2 L2 R2 B' R2 F U' F2 U' L2 B F2 U2 F2 U' F2\">B' U2 L2 R2 B' R2 F U' F2 U' L2 B F2 U2 F2 U' F2</span></p><p>B F2 U2 F // PS223</p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(B L2) // 223\">(B L2) // 223</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2 B U2 F' D2 F' D2 F2 U' R B D' B2 D L' R'\">U2 B U2 F' D2 F' D2 F2 U' R B D' B2 D L' R'</span></p><p>L2 B2 U' B U // PS223</p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(F U F' U2) // 223\">(F U F' U2) // 223</span></p>","zh":"<p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><strong>伪砖 (PSB)</strong></p><p>打乱为某状态的打乱的逆的状态称为该状态的<strong>逆状态</strong>. 以砖为单元形成的块称为伪砖 (PSB, Pseudo Block). 若n步转动序列<em>P</em>能还原伪砖的所有块, 则<em>P'</em>会在伪砖的逆情况制造一个砖. 称该伪砖为n步伪砖. 例如在打乱<em>X</em> = L2 B2 L2 R' B' U2 L' U2 L2 F2 U2 F' L2 F' D B2中, R B能还原223伪砖里的每个块. 那么对逆情况, 也就是打乱为<em>X'</em> = B2 D' F L2 F U2 F2 L2 U2 L U2 B R L2 B2 L2的状态, B' R'会制造出一个223砖. 实际应用是, 若在最少步项目途中遇到n步伪砖, 可先NISS然后做n步操作得到砖.</p><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">      <img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image8.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image6.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image10.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">      <img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image2.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p>打乱 = <em>X</em>, 转动R B还原223 PSB块</p></td><td><p>打乱 = <em>X'</em>, 转动B' R'会制造出223砖</p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tbody><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>1步伪砖实例</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image12.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image14.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PSF2L-1</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image16.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image18.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PS223</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image20.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image22.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PS123</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image24.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image26.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PS222</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image28.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image30.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PS122</p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image32.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image34.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">PS112</p></td></tr><tr><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td><td><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2, U'\"><strong>U2, U'</strong></span></p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>2步伪砖实例</strong></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image4.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image36.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td><td><p><img src=\"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/zh/image38.svg\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\"></p></td></tr><tr><td><p><strong>R B</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R2 B2</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>R' D</strong></p></td></tr></tbody></table></div><p><strong><u>实例</u></strong></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"F' D' B' D' F L2 D' L2 D L B L D\">F' D' B' D' F L2 D' L2 D L B L D</span></p><p>L' B' // PSF2L-1</p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(B') // F2L-1\">(B') // F2L-1</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"B' U2 L2 R2 B' R2 F U' F2 U' L2 B F2 U2 F2 U' F2\">B' U2 L2 R2 B' R2 F U' F2 U' L2 B F2 U2 F2 U' F2</span></p><p>B F2 U2 F // PS223</p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(B L2) // 223\">(B L2) // 223</span></p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"U2 B U2 F' D2 F' D2 F2 U' R B D' B2 D L' R'\">U2 B U2 F' D2 F' D2 F2 U' R B D' B2 D L' R'</span></p><p>L2 B2 U' B U // PS223</p><p><span class=\"tutorial-chip\" data-alg=\"(F U F' U2) // 223\">(F U F' U2) // 223</span></p>"},"algs":["U2, U'","F' D' B' D' F L2 D' L2 D L B L D","(B') // F2L-1","B' U2 L2 R2 B' R2 F U' F2 U' L2 B F2 U2 F2 U' F2","(B L2) // 223","U2 B U2 F' D2 F' D2 F2 U' R B D' B2 D L' R'","(F U F' U2) // 223"],"thumb":"/stats/tutorial/media/fmc-psb/en/image2.svg","warningCount":0,"hasImages":true,"hasTables":true}
